{
  "chapter": 197,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙入宫见小盘，小盘谈及冯劫批评秦律严苛却言之有理，欲任其为御史大夫，而让李斯出任廷尉掌律法。小盘又提牧场之战精彩，项少龙岔开话题问吕不韦如何推诿罪责。小盘告知太后朱姬搬往甘泉宫，关系转趋恶劣，且太后欲为嫪毐封侯并擢升其党羽，小盘无奈应允。项少龙建议顺水推舟，让嫪毐与吕不韦争权，坐山观虎斗。项少龙随后往找琴清，二人亲密之际，项少龙突然悟到太后搬离王宫或因有身孕。晚间邹衍归来，已完成《五德终始说》，欲托项少龙将来献书给小盘。邹衍自知阳寿将尽，与众人告别后准备返齐，此为最后一次相聚。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父认识冯劫这个人吗？他是专责我大秦律法的大夫。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "为何储君特别提起这个人来呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "此人颇有风骨，又不畏权势，连寡人他也敢出言顶撞。只是不知他是否受《吕氏春秋》的影响，竟忽然批评我大秦律法过于严苛，殊失圣人教化之义。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "如此说来，储君理应很不高兴才对。为何说起此人，反有欣然之意？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父最了解我，只因此人说及一些其他的事情，却非全无道理。例如他指出各国为君者，每根据形势变化，随时发布新政策，朝令夕改，使吏不知所守、民不知所趋，犯者则因法出多门而得售其奸，确是正论。所以法令必须一统，舍此再无强国之术。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我初时还以为他投向吕不韦，可是见他说话的轩昂神态颇肖师父你，后来又拿着你的盗贼申诉书严词诘问吕不韦，方知他只是像师父你的不怕死。哈！此人虽不宜掌律法，但却是当御史大夫的好料子。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "储君最好三思，李长史亦是个合适人选。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若说合适，最好由师父你来担任。你听过李斯正面顶撞过任何人吗？论识见，李斯十倍胜于冯劫，而其刑名之学，比之商鞅亦有过之而无不及。故他最适合做由他创出来的三公九卿里廷尉一职，出掌律法。而寡人亦可藉他之学，统一和强化全国律法，为将来一统天下打下坚实的根基。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小俊已把牧场一战详细告诉寡人，过程确是精彩绝伦，师父或许比白起还厉害。日后若师父领军出征，必可战无不胜。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "吕不韦如何推诿罪责？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然是审也不审便全体释放，再胡乱找些人来杀掉以首级充数，就不用愁我们认出身份来。若非有黑龙这一招，说不定我会召他进来，亲手把他干掉。哼！蒙骜罪该万死，幸好他还有两个好儿子。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "黑龙该制成了吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "幸好师父想出此一妙绝天下的计策，否则真不知如何可以压制吕不韦。嘿！我嬴政之有今日……",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "不要说这种话，储君乃上天注定一统天下的人物，微臣充其量只是玉成其事罢了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太后昨天搬往甘泉宫去！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "你是否和她争吵过呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "刚巧相反，近日我照师父吩咐，蓄意与太后修好。她坚持要搬往甘泉宫，我也曾苦苦挽留她，可是她却没有半点商量的余地，就那么说搬便搬，真是奇怪。嘿！其实她离宫更好，因为寡人可眼不见为净。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "她还有没有参加早朝会和议事呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这个她怎肯放手！虽不是常常出席早朝，但事无大小，均要先经她审阅，比以前更难应付。最气人的仍是嫪毐，这贼种气焰嚣张，一副太后代言人的神气，不但说话多了，还不断向太后打报告和搬弄是非，真恨不得把他一刀斩了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "既是如此，我们不若来招顺水推舟，把嫪毐变成太后的代言人。以这家伙的狼子野心，必会与吕不韦争权争个焦头烂额，我们便可坐山观虎斗。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可是我只要见到嫪毐，立即无名火起……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "若要成大事，必须有非常胸襟和手段，能人所不能。说到底，嫪毐仅是个小角色，顶多是结党营私，祸害远及不上吕不韦。只是有太后为他撑腰，才能搅风搅雨，且因他在别人眼中，始终是吕不韦一党，他若弄至神憎鬼厌，于吕不韦更无好处。储君还是多忍耐他几年吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父说得对。一天我未正式登位，仍要看太后脸色做人。嘿！太后离宫前要我把嫪毐封侯，我当时婉言拒绝。岂知太后由那天开始，便不肯在我签发的政令上加盖玺章，累得文牍积压。唉！看来只好如她所愿。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "这叫'识时务者为俊杰'，储君可向太后进言，待春祭之后，万象更新，方为嫪毐封侯赐爵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事情仍非这么简单，太后还要把嫪毐的几个奸党擢升要职。例如内史之位，嫪毐要由他的族人嫪肆接任。此外还有令齐、韩竭两人，一文一武，都是嫪毐新结的党羽，太后着我许他们出掌要职，想想便教人头痛。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "无论他如何扩张势力，始终难成气候。为得到太后支持，储君只好忍一时之气。何况！吕不韦要比储君的头更痛哩！",
      "tone": "安慰",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_pan",
      "speaker_name": "小盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不知为何，任何事落到师父手上，总变得轻轻松松的。师父的话，我当然言听计从。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "太后搬到甘泉宫一事，琴太傅听说了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我刚回府便知道，但因这趟太后带往甘泉宫的人，全是她的亲信，故少龙若要人家去调查，恐怕要叫少龙失望了。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "太后搬离王宫必有原因，真令人费解。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大人检点些好吗？下人会看见哩！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "这是惩戒你又唤我作项大人，琴太傅甘愿领罚吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真霸道！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qin_qing",
      "speaker_name": "琴清",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qin_qing",
      "text": "糟了！我想太后是有身孕哩！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "为了我们的俗事，竟要劳动干爹仙驾，我们这些小辈真……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙为何变得这么客气，更不用心中过意不去，因为老夫久静思动，正要返齐一行，好看望那群稷下旧友。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不用说，嫣然早请干爹代我们寻找柔姊，凭干爹在齐国的人脉关系，该是轻而易举的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "想不到我邹衍在风烛之年，仍可制造个新圣人出来，世事之出人意表者，莫过于此。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "干爹已完成了他的不世杰作《五德终始说》，还把它赐给我代他暂作保管。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "干爹想怎样处理《五德终始说》，尽管吩咐下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "将来黑龙出世之时，少龙你负责把此书献上给政储君，那比由老夫亲说更有力百倍。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "干爹不准备留到黑龙出世后才走吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "天数有定，干爹恐怕不能等那么久。今趟就算你们不来找我，我也会回来探看你们，然后顺道返齐。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "干爹！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "春去夏来，此乃天理常规，人生无常，仍只是自然之象，嫣然难道还看不通吗？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "干爹责怪得好！嫣然受教了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "'人有悲欢离合，月有阴晴圆缺'，干爹说得对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙比老夫看得更透彻。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "吕不韦仍有点气运，在储君加冕前，少龙至紧要忍让一点，避免与他正面交锋，那老夫就放心哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "干爹啊！我们这样制造一条黑龙出来，是否有点像在骗老天爷呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "确是有点取巧，但天命已明，新圣人正是由少龙一手培养出来的政储君。现在东方六国虽仍有点声势，却是不知自爱，只懂互相攻讦，日后只要政储君大权在握，六国灭亡之日，已是屈指可数。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "说到底干爹身为齐人，为何却一点不为己国的命运担心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "齐国只是老夫出生之地，老夫放眼却是统一后的天下。兼之现今齐襄王昏庸误国，只要想到他老夫就心中有气。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "干爹和嫣然都有同一看法，就是只有天下归于一主，人民方有和平安乐的日子。不过只要想起少龙说过'绝对的权力，使人绝对的腐化'两句话，就怕政储君将来会变质，再不若现在的知人善任、俯察下情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "只有当由人民推举领袖的制度出现后，情况才可以真个改变过来，不过那可是两千多年后的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "怎可能有这样的制度？夫君大人为何敢肯定是两千年后的事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "我只是随便猜估吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙常有惊人之语，盖因你非是普通人也，否则我这乖女儿不会对你死心塌地了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夜了！我也要早点休息，明天我便动程往齐国去。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 197,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    }
  ],
